# FlowDesk Design System

## Overview

The FlowDesk Design System establishes a consistent visual language and reusable UI components across the platform. It ensures that every screen follows the same design principles, creating a cohesive, intuitive, and professional user experience.

---

# Design Principles

FlowDesk is designed to be:

- Clean
- Modern
- Professional
- Friendly
- Accessible
- Responsive
- Consistent

The interface should reduce visual clutter while helping users complete tasks quickly and confidently.

---

# Brand Personality

FlowDesk should feel:

- Trustworthy
- Efficient
- Approachable
- Innovative
- Organised
- Vibrant without being overwhelming

