# Layout

## Maximum Width

```
1440px
```

---

## Grid

12-column responsive grid.

---

## Border Radius

| Component | Radius |
|------------|--------|
| Buttons | 10px |
| Cards | 16px |
| Inputs | 10px |
| Modals | 20px |

---

## Shadows

Cards should use soft shadows:

```
0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
```

---

# Spacing System

Use an 8-point spacing system.

| Size | Pixels |
|------|--------|
| XS | 4px |
| S | 8px |
| M | 16px |
| L | 24px |
| XL | 32px |
| XXL | 48px |
| XXXL | 64px |

---

# Buttons

## Primary Button

- Blue background
- White text
- Rounded corners
- Medium shadow

Examples:

- Save
- Login
- Register
- Create Booking

---

## Secondary Button

- White background
- Blue border
- Blue text

Examples:

- Cancel
- Back
- View Details

---

## Danger Button

- Red background
- White text

Examples:

- Delete
- Remove

---

## Success Button

- Green background
- White text

Examples:

- Confirm
- Complete

---

# Form Elements

Input fields should include:

- Rounded corners
- Clear labels
- Placeholder text
- Validation messages
- Focus state
- Error state

---

# Cards

Cards should include:

- White background
- Rounded corners
- Soft shadow
- Internal padding
- Optional icon
- Optional action button

Cards are used for:

- Statistics
- Customer summaries
- Reports
- Dashboard widgets

